column5: This is of a video of a cyclist in Russia who obviously had an angel on his shoulder  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=piL3JjuHB_w
Wow. Can you say 4 way stop ! I don't know which vehicle is in the wrong here, but that cyclist definitely has someone looking out for him.

Yep, that's about as close as it gets right there.  It's amazing how many of these videos there are on Youtube.  Once you start watching it's hard to stop clicking on the next one. Just one more turns into 2 am before you know it.
anyone seen the one where the motorcyclist rear ends a car on the highway, does a flip and lands on the roof of the car all while moving?
